OL,3,CTeachers and NHS staff to receive pay
OL,4,Crise, First Minister announces
OL,6,F"They want them to be fairly rewarded
OL,7,Ffor the vital work they do. These pay
OL,8,Fawards reflect how we value them and
OL,9,Frespect their hard work."
