OL,6,FLeader of the Welsh Conservatives,
OL,7,FAndrew RT Davies MS said: "It's
OL,8,Fclearly in the UK's national interest
OL,9,Fto end these strikes, but Labour
OL,10,Fministers in the Senedd allowed them
OL,11,Fto drag on.
OL,13,F"Unlike Labour ministers in the
OL,14,FSenedd, Welsh Conservatives will never
OL,15,Fprioritise vanity projects that
OL,16,Fdistract from our public services.
OL,18,F"Labour should also be prioritising
OL,19,Ffully funding our schools, NHS and
OL,20,Fhelping farmers to feed our nation."
